  1. Generates requested number of dreams
  2. Distribution across dream types matches config
  3. Each dream is a valid conversation with human and assistant turns
  4. Dreams reference identity context appropriately
  5. Handles API errors with retry and backoff

All 103 tests pass (27 new + 76 existing).

